snippet.title: Starship Chameleon for the TRS-80 CoCo
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

Dragon 32/64


Game description:

Starship Chameleon is an action somewhat similar to Kaboom!
Your goal is it to collect bombs before they reach the bottom. However, your starship has to be the exact same colour (blue or yellow). 
Also be aware of the bombs that will seek after you, you can NOT collect them and they will destroy the starship.
